                     <interp inst="t18300415-44-person548" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . The other had paid for the trousers, but they had not left the door; the prisoner appeared rather drunk - he was in work at the time at a lime wharf; his master has called on me, and given him a good character.</p>
